# Andy Lo ‚Äî Premium AI Website Creation

**Expert**: Andy Lo (@andylokcl) ‚Äî Co-founder of Proxa, AI Automation Agency  
**Domain**: Premium website creation using Google's free AI tools  
**Core Philosophy**: Treat AI tools like a production team ‚Äî each tool does ONE job excellently, then hands off cleanly to the next.

## What This Skill Does

Transforms website creation from a coding exercise into a **visual direction exercise**. You define the aesthetic ‚Üí AI generates the assets ‚Üí AI animates the motion ‚Üí AI assembles the site ‚Üí you deploy. The result: parallax, animated, CMS-powered websites that look like $10K-$20K agency work, built in hours, at zero tool cost.

## Key Frameworks

- **Tool Specialization Pipeline**: Nano Banana ‚Üí Flow ‚Üí Firebase Studio (each tool does one job)
- **Bookend Frame Architecture**: Define start + end frames, AI generates all motion between
- **Visual Direction First**: Establish aesthetic before touching any code
- **Progressive Polish Protocol**: Foundation ‚Üí pages ‚Üí content ‚Üí CMS ‚Üí polish ‚Üí deploy
- **Boilerplate-First Foundation**: Never start from scratch ‚Äî always begin with professional scaffolding

